    <p style="color:green"><b>NB:All members are expected to follow the rules and regualtions.Failure yo uphold the rules will lead to an automatic removal of the member from the group.<b></p>
  <ol>
 <i>1.Time management.</i><br>
     2.Respect all members of the group especially the leaders.<br>
     3.Always take part in group projects.<br>
     4.Always be present for group online meetings that is(Whatsapp)on Wednesdays and (Facebook) on Fridays.<br>
     5.Talk out any issue if you have one.<br>
     6.No addition of new members to the group unless verified by any of the group leaders.<br>
     7.Dress neatly<br>
     8.No drugs are allowed<br>
     9.No missing out on group activities unless you present a genuine apology to the group secretary<br>
